sub_title: Customer Success Manager V&D at Smartly.io
summary:
An enthusiastic and proactive young professional, with 8+ years of experience in different areas such as: project coordination, online marketing, international business development / analysis, customer relationship management, and strategic planning. Alongside living and professional experiences in Ecuador, USA, Germany, Spain and The Netherlands. 

•Fields of interest: Online Marketing, Technology, Business & Management, Strategic Planning, Sustainability.
